\sum_{i=1}^n
\frac{1}{i^2}
<
2 - \frac{1}{n}
LHS: \frac{1}{1}+\frac{1}{4}+\frac{1}{9}= \frac{49}{36}
RHS: 2-\frac{1}{3}=\frac{5}{3}
n = k
2-\frac{1}{k}
k+1
2-\frac{1}{k+1}
2-\frac{1}{k}+ \frac{1}{{k+1}^2}
\frac{1}{{k+1}^2}
2-\frac1k +\frac1{(k+1)^2} \le 2-\frac1{(k+1)}
\left( 2-\frac1{(k+1)}\right) - \left( 2-\frac1k +\frac1{(k+1)^2} \right)
